name: SF Salaries
data_intro: The original source for this data is [here](http://transparentcalifornia.com/salaries/san-francisco/). We've taken the raw files here and combined/normalized them into a single CSV file as well as a SQLite database with an equivalently-defined table.

cat_feature_intro.Benefits: - How are base pay, overtime pay, and benefits allocated between different groups?

num_feature_intro.Id: Have other ideas you're curious for someone else to explore? Post them in [this forum thread](https://www.kaggle.com/forums/f/977/sf-salaries/t/18264/sf-salaries-dataset).
